Acts ch. 267, sec. 2, effective July 13, 1990; and ch. 306, sec. 1, effective July 13, 1990. -- Amended 1988 Ky. Acts ch. 383, sec. 2, effective July 15, 1988. -- Amended 1986 Ky. Acts ch. 201, sec. 1, effective July 15, 1986. -- Amended 1980 Ky. Acts ch. 340, sec. 2, effective July 15, 1980. -- Amended 1978 Ky. Acts ch. 96, sec. 3, effective July 1, 1978. -- Amended 1962 Ky. metadata.lrc-note: (7/14/92). This section was amended by the 1992 Regular Session of the General Assembly and also repealed. Pursuant to KRS 446.260, the repeal prevails.
